            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬深周五近全日高位收市  全周升近1%至3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地3大指數以接近全日高位收市。通信服務、國資雲板塊上升，但貴金屬、銀行股下跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩市成交合計超過2萬億元(人民幣‧下同)，較上日增近兩成半至2.19萬億元。總結本周，滬指累計升0.97%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證指數最多跌11點或0.35%，低見3339點後喘定，大市回升，最多倒升30點或0.9%，高見3381點，全日收市報3379點，升28點或0.85%，成交8556.57億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指高開高走，隨後升幅進一步擴大，一度升返11000點，最多升209點或1.94%，高見11003點，全日收市報10991點，升196點或1.82%，成交1.34萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數報3978點，升49點或1.26%；創業板指數報2281點，漲55點或2.51%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">各板塊個別發展，電子訊息股漲逾3%；傳媒娛樂股升逾2%；汽車製造股升逾1%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期滬指升0.97%，深證成指及創業板指升逾2%及近3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14723332-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e5%91%a8%e4%ba%94%e8%bf%91%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e5%85%a8%e5%91%a8%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%911%e8%87%b33",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20181030_FI_A-SHARES_A%E8%82%A1_FB-3_source-ap_-4.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-21 16:20:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "韓股接近平收",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南韓股市收市變動不大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首爾綜合指數收報2654點，升不足1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">韓股全周升約2.4%。</p>\n</div>",
