            "title": "日股靠穩收市　全周跌近1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東京股市靠穩。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數收報38776點，升98點，升幅0.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股全周跌近1%。</p>\n</div>",
