        {
            "title": "台股高收1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台灣股市升約1%收市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">加權指數收報23730點，升242點，升幅1.03%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，台股累計升2.5%。</p>\n</div>",
